{"type":"message","id":"7545c2b7","parentId":"5884bec9","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:07:50.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"哎呀，搜索需要 Brave API 密钥呢 😯\n\n我没办法直接进行网页搜索啦，有几个方案可以解决哦~\n\n方案1：配置 Brave Search API 密钥 - 运行 `openclaw configure --section web` 来设置，配置好之后就可以随时用搜索功能啦 ✅\n方案2：使用 tavily-search 技能 - 如果安装了这个技能，可以用它来搜索，不需要额外配置 Brave 密钥 🔍\n方案3：你直接告诉我你想搜索什么内容，我可以帮你用其他方式查找哦 💡\n\n你想选哪个方案呢？或者你想搜索什么主题呀？😊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773706062198}}
{"type":"message","id":"09933f4d","parentId":"7545c2b7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:08:39.388Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54bdf69664a4c459a90ca909492\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 08:08 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54bdf69664a4c459a90ca909492]\nou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b: 帮我检查一下我的tavily search能不能使用？"}],"timestamp":1773706119387}}
{"type":"message","id":"923983ff","parentId":"09933f4d","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:08:42.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d4kcblj92o7rbgmvbsxyajnd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/tavily-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773706119388}}
{"type":"message","id":"4f7216ea","parentId":"923983ff","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:08:42.633Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d4kcblj92o7rbgmvbsxyajnd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tavily-search\ndescription: Tavily专业搜索引擎集成，提供高质量的网页搜索、新闻搜索、学术搜索功能。支持深度搜索、结果摘要、来源引用。当用户需要搜索最新信息、事实核查、查找资料时使用。\n---\n\n# Tavily Search 搜索引擎技能\n\n## 核心功能\n- 🔍 **网页搜索**：高质量全网搜索，返回最新、最相关的结果\n- 📰 **新闻搜索**：专门搜索最新新闻资讯，支持按时间范围过滤\n- 🎓 **学术搜索**：搜索学术论文、研究报告、专业资料\n- 📝 **智能摘要**：自动生成搜索结果的摘要，节省阅读时间\n- 📌 **来源引用**：所有结果都带原始来源链接，方便核实\n- 🌍 **多语言支持**：支持中英等多种语言搜索\n\n## 配置方法\n在配置文件中添加你的Tavily API Key：\n```yaml\ntavily:\n  api_key: \"your-tavily-api-key\"\n  max_results: 5  # 默认返回结果数量\n  search_depth: \"basic\"  # basic/advanced\n```\n\n## 使用示例\n```python\nfrom tavily import TavilyClient\ntavily = TavilyClient(api_key=\"your-api-key\")\nresponse = tavily.search(\"最新的AI技术发展趋势\", search_depth=\"advanced\")\nprint(response['answer'])  # 自动生成的摘要答案\nprint(response['results']) # 详细搜索结果列表\n```\n\n## 触发场景\n- 用户需要搜索最新的信息、新闻、资料\n- 需要事实核查、验证信息准确性\n- 查找专业知识、学术论文、技术文档\n- 需要获取带来源引用的可靠信息\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773706122632}}
