{"type":"message","id":"0af04e5d","parentId":"b4ea8fa2","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:21:31.502Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54bda650a4a4c2a12fb601621b5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 08:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54bda650a4a4c2a12fb601621b5]\nou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b: 我最近要买个冰箱，冰箱链接是【京东】https://3.cn/2H-w85Ve?jkl=@G1CPp0i97W07@ MF5681 「美的机皇550法式多门冰箱制冰」\n点击链接直接打开 或者复制文案打开京东，我需要你每天早上八点和晚上八点帮我全网查询价格 ，以卡片形式发送给我，看看是否是买入的时候。调用find skill查找下有没有相关的可以监测价格的skill"}],"timestamp":1773706891499}}
