{"type":"message","id":"95392f84","parentId":"b894b49f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:55:13.238Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-17 08:31:01 GMT+8] Exec completed (crisp-wi, code 1) :: - Resolving ecommerce-price-watcher [31m×[39m Rate limit exceeded (retry in 57s, remaining: 0/20, reset in 57s) Error: Rate limit exceeded (retry in 57s, remaining: 0/20, reset in…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54be283a88b8c2b01d6277d45e7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 08:55 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54be283a88b8c2b01d6277d45e7]\nou_0e5a587b08cd734c2cea1623133e9e3b: 两个要求:\n1. 调用价格监测skill时，需要同时在淘宝，京东，拼多多三个平台的官方旗舰店搜索同一款冰箱，并分别给我每个平台的最低价\n2. 等10分钟就再次安装ecommerce\\-price\\-watcher"}],"timestamp":1773708913237}}
{"type":"message","id":"9acdd81b","parentId":"95392f84","timestamp":"2026-03-17T00:55:25.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好的主人！收到两个要求，我记下来啦：📝\n\n1. 每次价格监测会同时搜索 **京东、淘宝、拼多多** 三个平台官方旗舰店，给出各平台最低价\n2. 我会在10分钟后重试安装 `ecommerce-price-watcher`\n\n我先设置个提醒，10分钟后自动安装。现在先来帮你搜索三个平台的价格看看：👇\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_izdb45ih9wthzq14qj6igl3c","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\LWS\\.openclaw\\workspace-my_robot_01\\search_all_platforms.py","content":"\nfrom tavily import TavilyClient\nimport yaml\nimport os\n\n# Expand home directory\nconfig_path = os.path.expanduser('~/.openclaw/config.yaml')\n\n# 读取配置\nwith open(config_path, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    config = yaml.safe_load(f)\n    \napi_key = config['web']['tavily']['api_key']\ntavily = TavilyClient(api_key=api_key)\n\n# 搜索三个平台\nproduct_name = \"美的机皇550法式多门冰箱 制冰 MR-550WUFIPZE\"\n\nplatforms = [\n    f\"美的550法式多门冰箱 制冰 京东官方旗舰店 最新价格\",\n    f\"美的550法式多门冰箱 制冰 淘宝官方旗舰店 最新价格\", \n    f\"美的550法式多门冰箱 制冰 拼多多官方旗舰店 最新价格\"\n]\n\nprint(\"=\" * 70)\nprint(f\"商品：{product_name}\")\nprint(\"搜索三大平台价格...\")\nprint(\"=\" * 70 + \"\\n\")\n\nall_results = []\nfor query in platforms:\n    print(f\"\\n【{query.split(' ')[2]}】\")\n    print(\"-\" * 50)\n    response = tavily.search(query, search_depth='advanced')\n    if response.get('answer'):\n        print(f\"摘要: {response['answer']}\")\n    else:\n        print(\"摘要: 无自动摘要\")\n    print()\n    for i, result in enumerate(response['results'][:2]):\n        title = result.get(\"title\", \"无标题\")\n        url = result[\"url\"]\n        content = result.get(\"content\", \"\")[:250]\n        print(f\"  {i+1}. {title}\")\n        print(f\"     链接: {url}\")\n        print(f\"     摘要: {content}...\")\n    all_results.append({\n        'platform': query.split(' ')[2],\n        'response': response\n    })\n    print()\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 70)\nprint(\"搜索完成\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773708913238}}
